---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import site from '../data/site.json';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — RentalHub"
  description="How RentalHub collects, uses, and protects your personal data. Compliant with India's Digital Personal Data Protection Act (DPDPA) 2023."
>

<section class="hero" style="min-height:35vh; padding-top:calc(var(--nav-h) + 3rem);">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width:700px;">
      <h1 class="hero-title" data-reveal>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub" data-reveal data-delay="100">
        Last updated: {site.legal.lastUpdatedPrivacy} · {site.legal.companyName}
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="legal-content">
      <p class="legal-meta">This Privacy Policy applies to {site.brand.name} ({site.legal.companyName}, "we," "us," or "our") and describes how we collect, use, share, and protect your personal information when you use our website (<a href={site.seo.siteUrl} style="color:var(--accent)">{site.seo.siteUrl}</a>) and services.</p>

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

      <h3>1.1 Information You Provide</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Registration data:</strong> Name, phone number, email address, city, and vehicle preferences when you register as a rider or rental partner.</li>
        <li><strong>Business information (partners):</strong> Business name, GST number, fleet size, vehicle types, and owner details provided during partner onboarding.</li>
        <li><strong>Communications:</strong> Messages, inquiries, and feedback you send through our contact form or email.</li>
        <li><strong>Newsletter subscriptions:</strong> Email address if you subscribe to our newsletter.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>1.2 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent, links clicked, browser type, device type, and operating system.</li>
        <li><strong>IP address and location:</strong> Approximate location derived from your IP address for city-based search and fraud prevention.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies and similar technologies:</strong> Session cookies for functionality and analytics. See Section 7 for details.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use your personal information to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Process your registration and create your account</li>
        <li>Connect you with rental shops or customers in your city</li>
        <li>Send booking confirmations, updates, and receipts</li>
        <li>Respond to your support requests and inquiries</li>
        <li>Improve our platform and personalise your experience</li>
        <li>Send platform updates and marketing communications (with your consent)</li>
        <li>Detect and prevent fraud, abuse, and security threats</li>
        <li>Comply with legal obligations and resolve disputes</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. How We Share Your Information</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your personal data. We may share your information with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Rental partners:</strong> When you book a vehicle, we share your name, phone number, and booking details with the rental shop to facilitate pickup and return.</li>
        <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> Third-party services we use to operate the platform (e.g., cloud hosting via Supabase, payment processing via Razorpay, analytics). These providers process data only as directed by us.</li>
        <li><strong>Legal authorities:</strong> If required by law, court order, or government regulation.</li>
        <li><strong>Business transfers:</strong> In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets, subject to standard confidentiality agreements.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Data Storage and Security</h2>
      <p>Your data is stored on secure servers in India (AWS Mumbai region via Supabase) with the following protections:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Encryption in transit (TLS 1.3) and at rest (AES-256)</li>
        <li>Row-level security policies restricting data access</li>
        <li>Regular security audits and penetration testing</li>
        <li>Access controls limited to authorised personnel only</li>
        <li>Automatic backups with 30-day retention</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Despite our best efforts, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

      <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Account data:</strong> Retained for the duration of your account plus 3 years after deletion</li>
        <li><strong>Booking records:</strong> Retained for 7 years for legal and tax compliance</li>
        <li><strong>Support communications:</strong> Retained for 2 years</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics data:</strong> Retained for 13 months in aggregated, anonymised form</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>6. Your Rights (DPDPA 2023)</h2>
      <p>Under India's Digital Personal Data Protection Act (DPDPA) 2023, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete data</li>
        <li><strong>Erasure:</strong> Request deletion of your personal data (subject to legal retention requirements)</li>
        <li><strong>Withdrawal of consent:</strong> Withdraw consent for marketing communications at any time</li>
        <li><strong>Grievance redressal:</strong> Raise a complaint with our Data Protection Officer</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href={`mailto:${site.contact.email}`} style="color:var(--accent)">{site.contact.email}</a>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>

      <h2>7. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use the following types of cookies:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Essential cookies:</strong> Required for the website to function (e.g., session management, theme preference). Cannot be disabled.</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> Help us understand how users interact with the site (PostHog). You can opt out by adjusting your browser settings.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings. Disabling essential cookies may affect site functionality.</p>

      <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>RentalHub is not intended for users under 18 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal data from minors. If we become aware that we have collected data from a minor, we will delete it promptly. Parents or guardians who believe their child has provided us with personal information should contact us at <a href={`mailto:${site.contact.email}`} style="color:var(--accent)">{site.contact.email}</a>.</p>

      <h2>9. Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites (e.g., rental shop websites, social media platforms). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties. We encourage you to review their privacy policies before providing any personal information.</p>

      <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we make significant changes, we will notify you via email (if you have registered) and update the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. Your continued use of RentalHub after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

      <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data, contact us:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href={`mailto:${site.contact.email}`} style="color:var(--accent)">{site.contact.email}</a></li>
        <li><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href={`tel:${site.contact.phone.replace(/\s/g,'')}`} style="color:var(--accent)">{site.contact.phone}</a></li>
        <li><strong>Address:</strong> {site.contact.address}</li>
        <li><strong>Company:</strong> {site.legal.companyName}</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
